Inditex Launches Designs for Southern Hemisphere, Isla Tells FT

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-05-23T01:25:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-23/inditex-launches-designs-for-southern-hemisphere-isla-tells-ft.html
Inditex SA (ITX) , owner of the Zara fashion
chain, has become the first global retailer to sell clothes
designed especially for the seasons of the southern hemisphere,
the Financial Times reported, citing an interview with Chairman
Pablo Isla.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 